               feloniously stealing, on the <rs id="t17860222-59-cd321" type="crimeDate">1st day of February</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17860222-59-off320 t17860222-59-cd321"></join>, four pounds nineteen shillings in monies numbered, the property of 
                     
                        <persName id="t17860222-59-victim713" type="victimName">
