                     <interp inst="t17860222-59-person717" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
             sworn.</p>
               <p>I am a patrol in Lincoln's-Inn-fields, I heard the prisoner say at the watch-house, he would pay the money belonging to 
               <persName id="t17860222-59-person718">
                  Edward
                   Taylor
               <interp inst="t17860222-59-person718" type="surname" value="Taylor"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17860222-59-person718" type="given" value="Edward"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17860222-59-person718" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            , which was four pounds nineteen shillings, at half a crown a week.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t17860222-59-person719">
                  CATHERINE
                   CLARK
               <interp inst="t17860222-59-person719" type="surname" value="CLARK"></interp>
